title: Man-Cave | Watch: Ronda Rousey looks ferocious in her training camp for UFC 193
text:
UFC 193 is coming up on November 14th, but to be honest we're not that excited.
We're not buying into Holly Holm as a potential challenger to Ronda Rousey's title.
However, we are looking forward to a fight that lasts longer than 16 seconds though, even if it's only a a few minutes.
Well, we were looking forward to that, but this video of Rousey's first week in training camp has us rethinking how long this thing is going to last.
Did it need the Montage Song? No, but are we happy that they did? Of course. Now, here'e the original.
